C                                                                               # Symmetry group
2                                                                               # Number of irreducible representations
Sigma+                                                                          # Irreducible representation label 1
8                                                                               # Nuclear spin degeneracy 1
Sigma-                                                                          # Irreducible representation label 2
8                                                                               # Nuclear spin degeneracy 2
5000.00                                                                         # Maximum temperature of linelist
0                                                                               # No. of pressure broadeners available
0                                                                               # Cooling function availability (1=yes, 0=no)
0                                                                               # Specific heat availability (1=yes, 0=no)
0                                                                               # Photo-absorption continuum cross-sections availability (1=yes, 0=no)
711                                                                             # No. of states in .states file
0                                                                               # Hyperfine resolved dataset (1=yes, 0=no)
1                                                                               # Uncertainty availability (1=yes, 0=no)
0                                                                               # Lifetime availability (1=yes, 0=no)
0                                                                               # Lande g-factor availability (1=yes, 0=no)
1                                                                               # No. of quanta cases
dcs                                                                             # Quantum case label
1                                                                               # No. of quanta defined
v                                                                               # Quantum label 1
I4 %4d                                                                          # Format quantum label 1
State vibrational quantum number                                                # Description quantum label 1
8908                                                                            # Total number of transitions
1                                                                               # No. of transition files
20218                                                                           # Maximum wavenumber (in cm-1)
NaN                                                                             # Higher energy with complete set of transitions (in cm-1)
